  "generation_notes": "Invoice is primarily a structured document, not prose. Line items section is hybrid: parse each line as 'description | quantity | unit price' and render as a table. Totals section is hybrid: compute subtotal = sum of qty * unit_price, tax = subtotal * tax_rate_percent / 100, total = subtotal + tax. Show each on its own row. Payment instructions is the only prose section and should be short."
